  "detailed_description": "Protect the streets from the living trash.<br><br>You have just arrived in the city to buy materials, only to see that it has been invaded by living trash.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561050/extras/a6f704d3a3666a0cc38c02c427820aa0.poster.avif?t=1770855058\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561050/extras/a6f704d3a3666a0cc38c02c427820aa0.webm?t=1770855058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561050/extras/a6f704d3a3666a0cc38c02c427820aa0.mp4?t=1770855058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Clean Street TD is a strategy game in which you have to defend the sewers from different types of garbage, build cleaning turrets which will help you defeat all your enemies, but carefully choose which upgrades you will buy, since each turret has a limit of two improvements.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Torretas</h2>Built with the materials you have on hand, although they do not have the best technology, they are everyone's best hope to stop the threat of living trash.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561050/extras/d68c5f107990a7835aae2003d99012a9.avif?t=1770855058\" width=320 height=320 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enemigos</h2>Experiments created by a mad scientist made garbage come to life and now they seek to cover all the sewers to flood the city.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561050/extras/bc1fba2de3f058743adce46f41a652a1.avif?t=1770855058\" width=320 height=320 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Each turret can choose two of four upgrades. Think about which one you'll need.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561050/extras/1f1b3d145e752ef83fff387117c341c7.avif?t=1770855058\" width=570 height=436 /></span><br></li><li>Enemies with unique abilities.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561050/extras/447af17b1bab758f22dff9fab8908541.poster.avif?t=1770855058\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561050/extras/447af17b1bab758f22dff9fab8908541.webm?t=1770855058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561050/extras/447af17b1bab758f22dff9fab8908541.mp4?t=1770855058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>Purchase permanent upgrades in the store<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561050/extras/71763282a0e219a4735be3655de27e2a.avif?t=1770855058\" width=570 height=320 /></span><br></li><li>An extra difficulty that you can customize<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561050/extras/4af3f08bbf60ca23e6ab486120daa002.avif?t=1770855058\" width=570 height=320 /></span></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Protect the streets from the living trash.<br><br>You have just arrived in the city to buy materials, only to see that it has been invaded by living trash.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561050/extras/a6f704d3a3666a0cc38c02c427820aa0.poster.avif?t=1770855058\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561050/extras/a6f704d3a3666a0cc38c02c427820aa0.webm?t=1770855058\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561050/extras/a6f704d3a3666a0cc38c02c427820aa0.mp4?t=1770855058\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Clean Street TD is a strategy game in which you have to defend the sewers from different types of garbage, build cleaning turrets which will help you defeat all your enemies, but carefully choose which upgrades you will buy, since each turret has a limit of two improvements.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Torretas</h2>Built with the materials you have on hand, although they do not have the best technology, they are everyone's best hope to stop the threat of living trash.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561050/extras/d68c5f107990a7835aae2003d99012a9.avif?t=1770855058\" width=320 height=320 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enemigos</h2>Experiments created by a mad scientist made garbage come to life and now they seek to cover all the sewers to flood the city.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561050/extras/bc1fba2de3f058743adce46f41a652a1.avif?t=1770855058\" width=320 height=320 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Each turret can choose two of four upgrades. Think about which one you'll need.<br><